Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero, Ivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A book full of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could read the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life.
