Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are supposed to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the name of the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu. The name of the girl who was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother used to read it to me when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
