Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest and I'm sure it'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such an irresponsible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty! I don't feel anything in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't use magic, {\i1}I'll{\i0\} protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, I will protect Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is what I want to do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No one is after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Square-class golem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This puppet really is like a devilish monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it, my beloved Myoz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Charlotte and her party doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They passed through the forest of Alden and are approaching the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the totem bell ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind that blows through the\NCarillon Canyon shall cry at your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter of my brother, Charles, who left her behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you lie bleeding on the ground, will my heart cry out in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Similar to when I killed Charles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Continue to keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a notice saying there's something suspicious going on at San Maron, near the border of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Gallia wouldn't just let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, invading through another's border is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's merely for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time to make use of the Great Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this too came originally from the eastern land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the artefacts we cannot tie to anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Colbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save them even at the cost of my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do with just the four of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to load that on the Ostland,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you the Musketeer Force's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope we don't have to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having slain the dragon, Ivaldi made his way deeper into the c... c{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...deeper into the cave where the room was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to be able to read a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're teaching me, I can pick up reading really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of Gandalfr's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you'll change, body and soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you are completely overtaken by Gandalfr's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You become a different person when you become Gandalfr?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So Saito's with me because he's Gandalfr?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So once I'm no longer a Void mage, it's over between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't use my magic anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then someone else will become the Void mage and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it feel like when you got out of your Gandalfr state?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it feel like? Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me! You should have felt a change in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you form a contract with me again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the border!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're over the bridge, we're in Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go right over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think you would be able to get away that easily, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylphid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find an opportunity to cross the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dages forter lis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Princess. I'm glad to see you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very brave to fight against this Jormungand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jormungand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iisan Hagaras.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but aren't here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, allow us to entertain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie! Take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time for the trump card to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. If you don't understand what I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then all I have to do is crush that carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out! She's after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Louise-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malicorn! Hurry and get us moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's not working after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:22.88,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Why did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Void mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the true power of a Void mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know yet that I can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you don't know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you it's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ostland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, I'll protect Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one you want, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let everyone else go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ful blisars ansul ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyofu need{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.22,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your magic's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to babysit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my plan to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. That's my role!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back to being the Zero Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worth being protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you weren't thinking about sacrificing yourself, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Great Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this thing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time! I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinard! Turn the handle and set the bearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche, you set the elevation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimli and Malicorn, prepare the shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.81,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "elevation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinard! Set the bearing to 45 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche! Elevation twenty degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.67,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, plug your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry with the next round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has Counter on its armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast Dispel on the shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to pierce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dispel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn mages!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Gandalfr, and you're with me only because I'm a void mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the contract good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the master can't use magic, the bond is practically gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say what's on your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or can't Gandalfr say what's he's really thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an aristocrat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worth anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Ivaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you with everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha will become your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast Dispel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ful blisars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.43,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ansul ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyofu need nousis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heilos iala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elpeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.73,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Void mage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you thinking all this by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this master and familiar crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been telling you that I love you from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not because you're Gandalfr?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me ask. What was that about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Tabitha being witty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really pitiful dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so scared of getting yelled at\Nby your favourite master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Speaking of you, you can't control the fact you love me so much, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just conditioned to love my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were all jealous and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity myself for how I developed feelings for my familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,getting controlled by the power of the Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'm doing this against my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness. We have disobeyed your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all ready to accept any kind of punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now give you your punishment for trespassing into Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A royal mantle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second in line for the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Void mage, work hard for Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return to you the mantle of a chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, Princess Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to say, welcome to Tristain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snuggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-i-to!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come down here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dog!
